{"id":206249,"date":[{"year":1950,"month":12,"day":4}],"page":"8","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"磁力","column":"","genre":"","count":"441","ytitle":"恶开(OK)曲:","mtitle":"奉劝美国迷","ftitle":"","authors":["卞之琳"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"卞之琳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开篇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大街坊，小西隣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来看穿美国流氓。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"讲起来有陈有新，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新的陈的都一样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈的完全真，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新的最可能。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“恶开”!我们不要紧；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活该!这些人可当心!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大有钱，小有财，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可别去向老美投靠!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们招你们过去住，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"剥光了撵回来:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“柏油也漆不像黑奴，滚你的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不成材黄皮肤!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们说“恶开!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那就是“活该!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大老板，小店东，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可别看美钞心动；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们招你们去合股，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一转眼踢出来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再不见自家的门户，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只好到垃圾桶里住；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们说“恶开!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那就是“活该!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大小姐，小姑娘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可别想做吉普女郎!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们接你们去跳舞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大清早赶出来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"衣裳变稀星糊涂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼上都眼泪模糊；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们说“恶开!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那就是“活该!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大懒虫，小傻瓜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可别盼“美援”来眼巴巴；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们餵你们洋馍馍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一下子钓上来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钓上来替他们当骆驼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炸药几顿在背上驮；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们说“恶开!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那就是“活该!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尾声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大街坊，小四邻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"算起来这已经是旧帐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就可恨“美国之音”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还要把死灰到处扬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别看像甜迷迷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闻闻看，火药气!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活该!那些人才相信；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“恶开”骗不了人民!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十一月八日"}]}